title: ROGERTHAT777
author: ROGERTHAT777
content: Hi guys.  I have many of these altcoins that have not even be dollarized yet.  I have one however that has a very good price on it that is showing on the ledger not the "poocoins" chart.  I understand some of those are scams and they eat up your fees.  I am wondeing if anyone has seen a scam on the ledger coins.  the official bssscan?I have tried to luqidity the altcoin into bnb and it just wasn't ready yet? no circulating supply.  The value listed is rather large and I am assuming I would just have to wait it out unless there is some other way than "swap" on the metmask app? thanks.

Maybe its a glitch. There are projects showing price even there is no trading or liquidity being used deployed. Can you share the name of the project that has value but liquidity isnt correct. Cause no matter what value it did represent its gonna be useless when the token traded on exchange has no trading volume, or enough liquidity for it to be exchange to other coins.

comments.author: Bttzed03
comments.body: Try to verify the price of that token in data aggregators such as Coingecko or Coinmarketcap. Under exchanges/markets tab, check what exchange is showing the most volume and the highest price. Sometimes, these tokens have little volume and price could be pumped easily with just $100.
